				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the modern day city, see <a href="Rome" title="Rome">Rome</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="Ancient_Rome_(disambiguation)" title="Ancient Rome (disambiguation)">Ancient Rome (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif/300px-Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif" width="300" height="285" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif/450px-Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif/600px-Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Roman_Republic_Empire_map_fast.gif" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Territories of the Roman civilization from 510 BC to 480 AD:
<div class="legend"><span class="legend-color" style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color: #a64; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;<a href="Roman_Republic" title="Roman Republic">Roman Republic</a></div>
<div class="legend"><span class="legend-color" style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color: #a6a; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;<a href="Roman_Empire" title="Roman Empire">Roman Empire</a></div>
<div class="legend"><span class="legend-color" style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color: #48a; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;<a href="Western_Roman_Empire" title="Western Roman Empire">Western Roman Empire</a></div>
<div class="legend"><span class="legend-color" style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color: #bc4; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;<a href="Eastern_Roman_Empire" title="Eastern Roman Empire" class="mw-redirect">Eastern Roman Empire</a></div>
