<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="Roman_army" title="Roman army">Roman army</a> (<i><a href="List_of_Roman_army_unit_types" title="List of Roman army unit types">unit types and ranks</a></i>, <i><a href="List_of_Roman_legions" title="List of Roman legions">legions</a></i>, <i><a href="Auxiliaries_(Roman_military)" title="Auxiliaries (Roman military)">auxiliaries</a></i>, <i><a href="List_of_Roman_generals" title="List of Roman generals">generals</a></i>)</td>
</tr>
