<li id="cite_note-221"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-221">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">William Cunningham (1900). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=C3kqAAAAYAAJ"><i>An Essay on Western Civilization in Its Economic Aspects: Mediaeval and modern times</i></a>. University Press<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=C3kqAAAAYAAJ">http://books.google.com/books?id=C3kqAAAAYAAJ</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 31 May 2012</span>.</span></span></li>
